---
// Full-bleed engraved frieze: Nashville, Athens of the South.
---

<figure class="relative">
  <div class="overflow-hidden" data-parallax>
    <img
      src="/images/parthenon-frieze.webp"
      alt="Engraved plate of Nashville's full-scale Parthenon replica at night, circuit traces rising from its roofline into a starfield"
      width="1536"
      height="1024"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      class="h-[52svh] w-full scale-[1.18] object-cover sm:h-[68svh]"
    />
  </div>
  <figcaption
    class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-7xl flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-8 gap-y-1 px-6 py-4 lg:px-10"
  >
    <span class="data">Centennial Park, Nashville</span>
    <span class="data text-gold-300">
      The society convenes in the Athens of the South, within sight of a
      full-scale Parthenon.
    </span>
  </figcaption>
  <hr class="rule-hair" />
</figure>
